import React from "react";
import { Box, Grid, Text, FlexAccordion, rem  } from "@mantine/core";
import { IconPhoto, IconPrinter, IconCameraSelfie } from '@tabler/icons-react';
const Home = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <Box
        h={40}
        w={`100%`}
        bg="gray.2"
        mt="xs"
        gap="md"
        justify="center"
        align="center"
      >
        <Text>Home</Text>
        <Text></Text>
        <Text></Text>
        <Text></Text>
      </Box>
      <Grid>
        <Grid.Col span={4}>
          <Box m="xs" bg="gray.2">
            <Flex
              mih={50}
              mt="xs"
              bg="indigo.5"
              gap="md"
              justify="center"
              align="center"
              direction="row"
              wrap="wrap"
            >
              <Text>Layout</Text>
            </Flex>

          </Box>
        </Grid.Col>
        <Grid.Col span={4}>2</Grid.Col>
        <Grid.Col span={4}>3</Grid.Col>
      </Grid>
    </>
  );
};

export default Home;
